通過行政命令解散現屆立法會，立即實行雙普選，朱凱廸認為是「重新點燃被遺棄的民主運動的一個好開端」。他續表示，11月區議會選舉，應集結公眾支持走向更具體的民主，例如2020年直選所有立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190721/s00001/1563680765241/【逃犯條例】朱凱廸憂激進行動難贏民心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190721%2Fs00001%2F1563680765241%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%86%82%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%A3%E8%B4%8F%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTecvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=ef40cf73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190721%2Fs00001%2F1563680765241%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%86%82%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%A3%E8%B4%8F%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83&h=627e23a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190721/s00001/1563680765241/【逃犯條例】朱凱廸憂激進行動難贏民心</a><br />\n==<br />\n屌你老母臭屄，乜屄都贏唔到，又嚟開始叫人散水，難你老母臭屄贏民心咩屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"咪成日淨睇標題啦"},{"pid":"8eb193e2bcdc9a950830c3d543a34872e24fc929","tid":1337392,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d48aae665f1f708a412783a767b655c253a686","tid":1337392,"uid":13242,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34232ec2b828593a7c04d754a29a5f763b64f35a","tid":1337392,"uid":9435,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:19:54.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆 <br />\n各有各做<br />\n唔駛理 <br />\n做自己覺得岩既事<br />\n冇大台<br />\n唔係佢講就岩既"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"依家係朱凱迪分化緊班前線同和平示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同7.1果時林鄭記招做嘅野有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"佢而家呢啲口吻咪即係又係大台囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f3a9f29e2f890e1835aeeaf7a70189c22916b8","tid":1337392