ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnHkbfQ.png&h=0c08e2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句，「要醒嘅人點都會醒」"},{"pid":"e50038ffcd8888f33d14adde956738d83785fd59","tid":1337392,"uid":263261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e8e23155111980d65384def5c3525f2af73b086e","tid":1337392,"uid":263261,"like":136,"dislike":7,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"佢不否定wo<br />\n仲要係明報<br />\n睇定d先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"人地講一句野比樓主放到咁大<br />\n話你唔係分化都好難令人相信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2fde7ff9cb00d577d03df122d0677800354e04","tid":1337392,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"雨傘運動贏撚晒光環啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ab69f603a36d0fad0deba9b496767583986008","tid":1337392,"uid":209865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc84292e2fc24d6c259f26762fcc0f2fb67b630a","tid":1337392,"uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"日月神報 facebook 留言，原來都幾多正常人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出少句聲當幫忙 好嗎?<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪驚自己之後選舉無票姐？ :p<br />\n<br />\n左膠又派膠<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，你泛民呢種不痛不癢、搞左幾十年都係廢的抗爭先係失盡民心。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱迪唔算「泛民」而係左膠😁<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦明報！<br />\n<br />\n唔通企定定畀人扑呀？ 首先用暴力嘅係警察，首先係政府的暴政， 簡直 本末倒置<br />\n<br />\n選舉近了，是教人現真身。<br />\n<br />\n呢家仲講民意？乜民意有成功向政府施壓？<br />\n<br />\n和平左廿年 甘得到咩野?<br />\n<br />\n朱生你d左膠咁耐都重唔明民心根本唔係求返黎？<br />\n<br />\n明報又想帶風向？<br />\n<br />\n神係你！<br />\n鬼又係你！<br />\n<br />\n又做民意代表？<br />\n<br />\n點呀！共匪激進你唔擔心下？<br />\n<br />\n天滅左膠<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪要做阿叻？<br />\n<br />\n張超雄後另一, 飯民係咪決定交佢出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n又黎<br />\n<br />\n靠你地膠足30幾年就搞成香港宜家咁lor<br />\n<br />\n朱八戒要大家變回和理非非<br />\n<br />\n越黎越多人支持&amp;不割席<br />\n<br />\n不如比個方法出嚟先？十幾萬一個月。<br />\n<br />\n其實支撐抗爭者既係公平正義，唔係民心<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆呀豬隊友！成日出黎潑冷水！<br />\n<br />\n7月1日唔衝立法會，乜惡法都已經過晒<br />\n<br />\n妖，收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"民意可以保到個議員位<br />\n袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9350902fb1f9d995cd933eb17ca89695ae1eee70","tid":1337392,"uid":151623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔好正負平由佢沉得唔得"},{"pid":"ce6c0d5e3f56e4cce12b2a8c2e63dbac0465a701","tid":1337392,"uid":197470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"477e8f753ff009cc6a6a15b4ce33edcdac3c0273","tid":1337392,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"[721]敵我分析, 後續戰略改變, 分工及改善建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5fe367ae12e3eb9aa880167a5aaa05a21dae344","tid":1337392,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6c0d5e3f56e4cce12b2a8c2e63dbac0465a701","tid":1337392,"uid":197470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:45:49.000Z","msg":"係要贏，然後自然有民心"},{"pid":"aeea633dfcd3785c213fcd22e34b0b40b9f9d760","tid":1337392,"uid":249526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:48:52.000Z","msg":"各有各做"},{"pid":"220cf2630a47cda35407e35b18f1e5888b9f67e8","tid":1337392,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"[快閃活動］狗屋外牆翻新，以及爬蟲藝術館<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d54da426a9aa1446e00732e02bdd4bf90070edc6","tid":1337392,"uid":63808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"麻煩搞一搞元朗d嚴重鄉黑"},{"pid":"4919ea43f940bad91f8f20df417800139f4f1a9a","tid":1337392,"